libs.content:
find_library(tbb_${_comp}_library_debug ${_comp}_debug
          hints ${tbb_library} ${tbb_search_dir}
          paths ${tbb_default_search_dir} env library_path
          path_suffixes lib)

find_program(wrap_cmd names wrap 
    paths "${_gtsam_wrap_dir}" ${cmake_install_prefix}/bin "$env{home}/bin" /usr/local/bin /usr/bin
    doc "wrap executable location")

find_library(cppunitlite_libs names cppunitlite
  hints "${_gtsam_lib_dir}" ${cmake_install_prefix}/lib "$env{home}/lib" /usr/local/lib /usr/lib
  doc "cppunitlite libraries")

find_library(hwloc_hwloc_library
	names hwloc
	hints ${hwloc_dir}
	path_suffixes lib lib32 lib64)

find_library(
    fftw_lib
    names "fftw3"
    paths $env{fftwdir}
    path_suffixes "lib" "lib64"
    no_default_path
  )

find_library(
    fftwf_lib
    names "fftw3f"
    paths $env{fftwdir}
    path_suffixes "lib" "lib64"
    no_default_path
  )

find_library(
    fftwl_lib
    names "fftw3l"
    paths $env{fftwdir}
    path_suffixes "lib" "lib64"
    no_default_path
  )

find_library(adolc_libraries 
  adolc 
  paths $env{adolcdir} ${lib_install_dir} 
  path_suffixes lib lib64)

find_library(computecpp_runtime_library
  names computecpp computecpp_vs2015
  hints $env{computecpp_dir}
  path_suffixes lib
  doc "computecpp runtime library")

find_library(computecpp_runtime_library_debug
  names computecpp_d computecpp computecpp_vs2015_d
  hints $env{computecpp_dir}
  path_suffixes lib
  doc "computecpp debug runtime library")

find_program(computecpp_info_executable computecpp_info
  hints $env{computecpp_host_dir}
  path_suffixes bin
  no_system_environment_path)

find_library(metis_metis_library
      names metis
      hints ${metis_dir}
      path_suffixes lib lib32 lib64)

find_library(gsl_gsl_library
    names libgsl.dll.a gsl libgsl
    paths  ${gsl_possible_root_dirs}
    path_suffixes lib
    doc "gsl library" )

find_library(gsl_gslcblas_library
    names libgslcblas.dll.a gslcblas libgslcblas
    paths  ${gsl_possible_root_dirs}
    path_suffixes lib
    doc "gsl cblas library dir" )

find_program(mex_command mex
      paths ${wrap_custom_matlab_path} env path
      no_default_path)

deps.context:
find_package(
      python default
      components interpreter development
      exact)
